        <item>
            <title>Version 2.4.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>ForgedBrew 2.4.1</h2>
                <p>Enhanced Trust Management and Homebrew security scanning ahead of Homebrew's September 1, 2026 cask-quarantine change: faster and more accurate scans (no false alarms on large apps, online notarization recognized, saved results with Re-scan, and CVSS severity ratings). Plus other cleanup and refinement: reliable installs from every screen, Cmd-Q quits, more accurate update detection, better search, and a documentation and QA hardening pass.</p>
            ]]></description>
